	Rewrite to...
	(ios_dev_file_pread, ios_dev_file_pwrite): ...this.
	* src/ios-dev-mem.c (ios_dev_mem_getc, ios_dev_mem_putc): Rewrite
	to...
	(ios_dev_mem_pread, ios_dev_mem_pwrite): ...this.

